      "style": "light",
      "content": "合併症ファーストで薬を選ぶ3つのステップ",
      "html": "<style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#0a2e2e;display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:relative}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:20px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);color:#0d6e6e;font-size:15px;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px}.logo{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0d6e6e}.section-label{font-size:15px;color:#14b8a6;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;padding:0 60px;margin-top:10px}.main{flex:1;display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 60px}.left-panel{flex:1}.left-panel h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:28px;color:#0a2e2e}.list-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:20px;margin-bottom:20px}.list-num{background:#14b8a6;color:#fff;font-size:26px;font-weight:900;width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}.list-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#1a3a3a;padding-top:6px}.list-text strong{color:#0d6e6e}.footer{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:14px;color:rgba(10,46,46,0.4)}</style><div class=\"slide\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">SLIDE 5/8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"section-label\">結 ── 実践</div><div class=\"main\"><div class=\"left-panel\"><h2>明日からの実践アクション</h2><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">1</span><span class=\"list-text\"><strong>心血管既往・肥満の確認</strong> → 該当すればGLP-1 RA（経口セマグルチド）を優先</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">2</span><span class=\"list-text\"><strong>チルゼパチド導入前にDPP-4阻害薬を中止</strong> → 切り替え忘れに注意</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">3</span><span class=\"list-text\"><strong>CKD/心不全/ASCVDにはSGLT2阻害薬</strong> → HbA1c目標達成済でも心腎保護で追加</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">4</span><span class=\"list-text\"><strong>初診時チェック:</strong> eGFR, uACR, BNP, BMI, 心血管既往 → 薬剤選択に直結</span></div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
