      "title": "Take Home Message",
      "style": "accent",
      "content": "3つの持ち帰りポイント",
      "html": "<style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d4a4a,#14b8a6);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#fff;display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:relative}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:20px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);color:#fff;font-size:15px;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px}.logo{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#fff}.main{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:0 60px;gap:24px}.main h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:center}.thm-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:16px;padding:28px 36px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px}.thm-num{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);min-width:50px}.thm-text{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.4}.footer{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)}</style><div class=\"slide\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">SLIDE 6/8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>Take Home Message</h2><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">01</span><span class=\"thm-text\">心血管既往・肥満がある2型DMには、GLP-1 RA（経口薬）を積極的に選択</span></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">02</span><span class=\"thm-text\">DPP-4阻害薬とGLP-1 RA/GIP-GLP-1 RAの併用は禁忌。切り替え時は必ず中止</span></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">03</span><span class=\"thm-text\">「HbA1cを下げる」から「合併症で薬を選ぶ」時代へ。心腎保護を意識した処方を</span></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
